[[Alkan|Talkanin]], [[Alkin|Tilkinin]], [[Alkyn|Talkynin]] yakk d tizrarin isnullin yemgaraden deg igmanen-is s wazal n 10, 12, 14 i yal tigget n [[Takura tabelkamt|tkura tabelkamt]] s [[asnay|wesnay]]
Amdya: Tazrart n [[Alkin|tilkinin]] tessentu (tbeddu) s [[Amitan|Umitan]] (CH<sub>4</sub>), ɣer [[itan]] (C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub>), [[Apṛupan|Prupan]] (C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>8</sub>), [[Abutan]] (C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>10</sub>), [[Pintan]] (C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>12</sub>)

[[Uddis akruran|uddisen]] yellan deg yal tazrart zdint deg Yiwet n tegrawt tameẓyant n [[abelkim|ibelkimen]] yettusemman [[tagrawt tamesɣant]]
